(290, 1, '2018-04-23 14:40:02', '2018-04-23 13:40:02', '<p>[vc_row css_animation="" row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="full_width" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern"][vc_column][qode_elements_holder number_of_columns="three_columns"][qode_elements_holder_item item_padding="21% 20%" vertical_alignment="middle" advanced_animations="no" item_padding_1024_1280="18% 17%" item_padding_768_1024="16% 18%" item_padding_600_768="18% 27%" item_padding_480_600="16% 20%" item_padding_480="14%"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h5><span style="color: #f95c55;">I am</span></h5>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="4px"][vc_column_text]I''m Morena Fiore, a web developer based in Tottenham, North London with 10 years experience. I''ve worked for a variety of clients, from small startups to worldwide agencies, building responsive websites and hybrid apps.I''m a hard working and flexible individual, I easily adapt to any project and technology at any stage of the development.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="15px"][/qode_elements_holder_item][qode_elements_holder_item background_color="#f6f6f6" item_padding="21% 20%" vertical_alignment="middle" advanced_animations="no" item_padding_1024_1280="18% 17%" item_padding_768_1024="16% 18%" item_padding_600_768="18% 27%" item_padding_480_600="16% 20%" item_padding_480="14%"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h5><span style="color: #f95c55;">IMake</span></h5>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="4px"][vc_column_text]I specialise in UI work and WordPress websites.As a contractor developer, I can support teams and projects of any size, from sole UI work, to supporting backend (PHP with WordPress) or JavaScript devs, with React knowledge.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="15px"][/qode_elements_holder_item][qode_elements_holder_item item_padding="21% 20%" vertical_alignment="middle" advanced_animations="no" item_padding_1024_1280="18% 17%" item_padding_768_1024="16% 18%" item_padding_600_768="18% 27%" item_padding_480_600="16% 20%" item_padding_480="14%"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h5><span style="color: #f95c55;">My Story</span></h5>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="4px"][vc_column_text]I trained as PHP developer at Mind Unit in 2008, then worked on a variety of projects as a contractor, including API integration work, WordPress websites and complex plugins. I''ve worked at HeathWallace for 5 years building websites for the financial sector, as well as React apps. I''ve focused on extensive browser list compatibility as well as accessibility.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="15px"][/qode_elements_holder_item][/qode_elements_holder][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="parallax" parallax_content_width="in_grid" text_align="center" background_image="294" full_screen_section_height="no"][vc_column][vc_empty_space height="105px"][vc_row_inner row_type="row" type="full_width" text_align="center" css_animation=""][vc_column_inner width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-3"][vc_single_image image="25" img_size="full" alignment="center" qode_css_animation=""][counter type="zero" box="no" position="center" separator="no" digit="10950" font_color="#ffffff" text="Cups of coffee &amp; tea" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_empty_space height="40px"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-3"][vc_single_image image="26" img_size="full" alignment="center" qode_css_animation=""][counter type="zero" box="no" position="center" separator="no" digit="10" font_color="#ffffff" text="Years of experience" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_empty_space height="40px"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-3"][vc_single_image image="27" img_size="full" alignment="center" qode_css_animation=""][counter type="zero" box="no" position="center" separator="no" digit="50" font_color="#ffffff" text="+ Projects" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_empty_space height="40px"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner