(397, 1, '2018-04-03 21:48:37', '2018-04-03 20:48:37', '[vc_row css_animation="" row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="full_width" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern"][vc_column][qode_elements_holder number_of_columns="three_columns"][qode_elements_holder_item item_padding="21% 20%" vertical_alignment="middle" advanced_animations="no" item_padding_1024_1280="18% 17%" item_padding_768_1024="16% 18%" item_padding_600_768="18% 27%" item_padding_480_600="16% 20%" item_padding_480="14%"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h5><span style="color: #f95c55;">I am</span></h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="4px"][vc_column_text]I''m Morena Fiore, a web developer based in Tottenham, North London with 10 years experience. I''ve worked for a variety of clients, from small startups to worldwide agencies, building responsive websites and hybrid apps.\r\n\r\nI''m a hard working and flexible individual, I easily adapt to any project and technology at any stage of the development.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="15px"][/qode_elements_holder_item][qode_elements_holder_item background_color="#f6f6f6" item_padding="21% 20%" vertical_alignment="middle" advanced_animations="no" item_padding_1024_1280="18% 17%" item_padding_768_1024="16% 18%" item_padding_600_768="18% 27%" item_padding_480_600="16% 20%" item_padding_480="14%"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h5><span style="color: #f95c55;">IMake</span></h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="4px"][vc_column_text]I specialise in UI work and WordPress websites.\r\n\r\nAs a contractor developer, I can support teams and projects of any size, from sole UI work, to supporting backend (PHP with WordPress) or JavaScript devs, with React knowledge.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="15px"][/qode_elements_holder_item][qode_elements_holder_item item_padding="21% 20%" vertical_alignment="middle" advanced_animations="no" item_padding_1024_1280="18% 17%" item_padding_768_1024="16